post_text:
ESS Southern Utah recently selected one of their local substitute teachers, Gerlinde Braunberger, as their prestigious 2019 Impact Award recipient. They recently presented her with a $500 check along with another $500 check for the school of her choosing (Snow Canyon High). Congratulations Gerlinde!
@ESS Southern Utah
@ESS Education Staffing

